---

7. Security Model

7.1 ZK Security Guarantees

No raw data exposure

No correlation between proofs

Proofs cannot be faked or replayed

Salt protects against data reconstruction


7.2 Contract-Level Protections

Rate limits

Anti-replay

Per-user validation windows

Strict proof formats



---

8. Implementation Details

8.1 Circom Circuit (EnergyProof)

Validates:

percentage = ((previousReading – currentReading) / previousReading) * 100

Ensures:

percentage >= 15%

All without revealing raw readings.

8.2 Smart Contracts

Hardhat workflow

Qubic deterministic compute pipeline

Modular verifier interface


8.3 Frontend

React/Vite prototype includes:

Proof generator

BLq tracker

Leaderboard

Celestial theme for judges/demo clarity



